NAME
        location
        location [where you live]
        location -clear

DESCRIPTION
        This command is available so you can set your location in
        real life so others can see it while using the finger command.
        It is not necessary to set your location.  Please do not
        put offensive names in this field or you run the risk of
        losing your character.

SYNTAX
        location
                Shows your current set location, if any.

        location [where you live]
                Sets your location to [where you live]

        location -clear
                Removes your set location.

SEE ALSO
	email, name, birthday, icq, webpage.
